               <p>JOHN ROLLS. I lost a handkerchief and brush on the 29th of April; I had seen them safe when I was going to bed that night, lying on the locker of the bar, and missed them next morning.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280529-21-person209">
                  JANE 
                  BAKER
